## Tableaux Proving

```elixir
import ShotDs.Hol.Sigils
import ShotTx.Prover
```

```elixir
res = ~f"![P:$i>$o, Q:$i>$o]: ((?[X:$i]: P @ X & Q @ X) => (?[X:$i]: P @ X) & (?[X:$i]: Q @ X))"
|> prove
format_result res
```

```elixir
render res
```

$\exists X. X$

```elixir
res = ~f"?[X: $o]: X" |> prove
format_result res
```

```elixir
render res
```

$a \land b \supset a$

```elixir
res = ~f"a & b => a" |> prove
format_result res
```

```elixir
render res
```

$a \supset a \lor b$

```elixir
res = ~f"a => (a | b)" |> prove
format_result res
```

```elixir
render res
```

**Cantor:** $\nexists F. \forall Y. \exists X. F X = Y$

```elixir
res = ~f"~?[F : $i>$i>$o]: ![Y: $i>$o]: ?[X: $i]: F @ X = Y"
|> prove()
format_result res
```

```elixir
render res
```

**Extensionality:** $p (a \land b) \supset p (b \land a)$

```elixir
res = ~f"p @ (a & b) => p @ (b & a)" |> prove
format_result res
```

```elixir
IO.puts ShotTx.Proof.to_text elem res, 1
```

```elixir
render res
```

**Extensionality:** $\forall X Y. p~X \land p~Y \supset p (X \land Y)$

```elixir
res = ~f"![X : $o, Y : $o]: p @ X & p @ Y => p @ (X & Y)" |> prove
format_result res
```

```elixir
render res
```

**Finite domain of type $o\to o$**

```elixir
res = ~f"""
(
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: X) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: ~X) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: $false) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: $true)
)
=>
![Y : $o>$o]: p @ Y
"""
|> prove
format_result res
```

```elixir
render res
```

```elixir
res = ~f"""
(
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: X) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: ~X) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: $false) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: $true)
)
=>
?[Y : $o>$o]: ~ p @ Y
"""
|> prove
format_result res
```

```elixir
render res
```

```elixir
res = ~f"p @ a & p @ b => p @ (a & b)" |> prove
format_result res
```

```elixir
render res
```

```elixir
res = ~f"p @ a & q @ a => ?[X : $i>$o]: X @ a & X @ b" |> prove
format_result res
```

```elixir
render res
```

```elixir
res = ~f"p @ a & q @ b => ?[X : $i>$o]: X @ a & X @ b & X != (^[Y: $i]: $true)"
|> prove
format_result res
```

```elixir
render res
```

